          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Look for Utah state licensing, liability insurance, a written satisfaction guarantee, experience with Southern Utah-specific pests (bark scorpions, subterranean termites), eco-friendly treatment options, and strong online reviews. Certifications like QualityPro and BBB accreditation are additional trust signals.</p>
