        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">How often should I schedule pest control in St. George?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Quarterly service is the standard for year-round protection in Southern Utah's warm climate. High-pressure situations like active scorpion infestations or termite activity may require monthly service initially, then transitioning to quarterly once the problem is controlled.</p>
